(1, 1, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Bacalah teks berikut untuk mengerjakan soal nomor 1 dan 2</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 18.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">(1)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Selain tak mandiri, pengelolaan sumber daya alam juga cenderung mengabaikan kelestarian.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 18.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">(2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Pohon yang dibabat jauh lebih banyak dari yang ditanam</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 18.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">(3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Pembukaan lahan perkebunan atau pertanian dengan membakar hutan.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 18.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">(4)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Menangkap ika dengan menggunakan bom. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt; line-height: normal; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 18.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">(5)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Sementara itu pejabat korup dengan mudah memberikan konsesi pemanfaatan hutan tanpa memperdulikan daya dukung dan kelestarian lingkungan.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 14.2pt;\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">(</span><a href=\"http://ekonomi.kompas.com/read/2017/09/07/051546726/susi-dan-tiga-pilar-yang-tak-sekadar-mitos\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">http://ekonomi.kompas.com/read/2017/09/07/051546726/susi-dan-tiga-pilar-yang-tak-sekadar-mitos</spa